Class MRNA

java.lang.Object
  gffParser.GFF3
      gffParser.MRNA
All Implemented Interfaces:
IDHolder
public class MRNA
extends GFF3
implements IDHolder

The MRNA class decorates a GFF3 It adds methods to retrieve the unique ID and to establish child relationships with other GFF3 objects (MRNA-StartCodon,MRNA-StopCodon,MRNA-CDS,MRNA-Exon)

Author:
Vinny
